title: How to learn React Native?
content: JavaScript is the world's most popular programming language JavaScript is the programming language of the Web javascript is easy to learn.
ponit1: Create native apps for Android, iOS, and more using React.
ponit2: React Native combines the best parts of native development with React, a best-in-class JavaScript library for building user interfaces.
titleEnd: Perfect for learning how the react native works, prototyping a new idea, or creating a demo to share online.
